	CALL MESSAGE_TALK(2, TALKER:0, TALKER:1)
ELSEIF 연회장소재판정(MASTER)
	CALL MESSAGE_TALK(1)
ELSEIF TALENT:MASTER:형상 == 4 && TIME > 1140 && CFLAG:MASTER:데이트중 && (CFLAG:MASTER:현재위치 % 100) % 10 && CFLAG:MASTER:현재위치 != OMANEKIBEYA()
